        "content": "# 🚀 Automated Trend-Based Content Generator\n\nThis workflow turns daily Google Trends into ready-to-post content for Blog, Instagram, and TikTok using AI Agents.\n\n## ⚡️ How it works\n1. **Scout:** Fetches Google Trends and selects the best viral topic.\n2. **Create:** Generates an SEO Blog, Carousel slides, and a Script simultaneously.\n3. **Approve:** Sends drafts to Slack. Click \"Approve\" to save to Google Sheets.\n\n## 🛠 Setup Requirements\n- **OpenAI API Key** (GPT-4o recommended)\n- **Slack Account** (for notifications)\n- **Google Sheets** (for storage)"
